Two female soccer players are in a competitive chase for the ball during a soccer match. To the right is a player wearing a white jersey with black lettering, and black shorts with white lettering. She has her foot connected to the ball, and is hunched over with her arms braced in front of her. Her mouth is wide open and her eyes are closed. She is facing towards the right of the frame. Behind her is another player in an all blue uniform with white lettering. This player has her eyes locked onto the back of the other player, and has her mouth set into a downturned scowl. Neither of her feet are touching the ground, and one ankle is bent at an angle to suggest that she is falling. She has one arm braced on the girl wearing black and white, and the other is pulled back with her palm open. Two of the girls teammates appear blurry in the background, but are approaching the two trying to get the ball. Also pictured in the background is a tall red flag, and behind that is a wall of trees.

City pedestrians walk by a "Puppet Theatre" cart on a busy day. The Puppet Theater cart is slightly taller than the average person, and not very wide. It is covered in yellow, purple, green, pink, and blue paint that cascade down the front of the cart in waves. Also pictured on the cart are two hand painted sunflowers. The cart is located on the corner of a busy city intersection, and is positioned below a vertically standing stop light. To the left of the cart are a man and a woman. The man is dressed casually, in a brown jacket and jeans, while the woman is dressed professionally, wearing a white turtle neck and gray trench coat. The man is looking away from the camera, while the woman is looking towards it. In the background there are several large skyscrapers, and the sky itself is obscured by these buildings. In the street there are dozens of people crossing the intersection, with two white cars bearing navy blue stripes waiting for the light to turn green.
